---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sport"
  description="Fencing since age 6. Cyprus national champion across every age category. First Cypriot to reach Top 32 at European and World Championships at Cadet level."
>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="sport-hero">
        <div class="sport-hero-text">
          <span class="section-label">Sport</span>
          <h1>Fencing since age&nbsp;6</h1>
          <p class="sport-lead">
            Fencing has been the spine of my life since I was six years old. My father
            brought the sport to Cyprus and founded its first club. I was always going to
            fence. What I didn't expect was how far it would take me.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sport-hero-img">
          <img
            src="/images/alex-fencing-bw.jpg"
            alt="Alexandros fencing in competition"
            width="480"
            height="560"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- Career highlights -->
      <div class="sport-content container--narrow">
        <h2>Career highlights</h2>

        <ul class="highlights-list">
          <li>Started fencing aged 6 at my father's club — the first fencing club in Cyprus</li>
          <li>Cyprus Champion in every age category, all the way through to U21</li>
          <li>Member of the Cyprus National Fencing Team (Épée)</li>
          <li>Competed internationally across Europe and beyond, supported by the Cyprus Fencing Federation and the Bank of Cyprus</li>
          <li class="highlight-featured">
            <strong>First Cypriot to reach the Top 32 at both the European and World Championships at Cadet level</strong>
          </li>
          <li>National Fencing Referee (Épée) since 2024 — officiating national-level competitions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- Photo gallery -->
      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h2 class="gallery-title">From the piste</h2>
        <div class="gallery">
          <div class="gallery-item gallery-item--wide">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-1.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros in fencing competition"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-2.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros competing in épée"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-3.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros at a fencing tournament"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-4.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros in fencing gear"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-with-father.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros with his father at a fencing event"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item gallery-item--accent">
            <img
              src="/images/alex-fencing-age-7.jpg"
              alt="Alexandros fencing aged 7"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <span class="gallery-caption">Age 7. Already serious about it.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- Current status -->
      <div class="sport-content container--narrow">
        <h2>Right now</h2>
        <p>
          In July 2025, I fractured my right metacarpal — my sword hand — and had two
          surgical nails in for three months. I haven't trained fencing since. Moving to
          Nicosia for university has added another layer of distance from the sport, for
          now.
        </p>
        <p>
          I intend to get back on the piste. The question is when, not if. In the
          meantime, the gym keeps the physical discipline that fencing built from
          disappearing entirely.
        </p>

        <div class="goals-box">
          <span class="goals-label">Goals</span>
          <ul class="goals-list">
            <li>Return to fencing when circumstances allow</li>
            <li>Maintain the conditioning built over years of elite training</li>
            <li>Long-term: continue competing, potentially move into higher-level refereeing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .sport-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .sport-lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .sport-hero-img img {
    width: 320px;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
    filter: grayscale(15%);
  }

  /* Content sections */
  .sport-content {
    padding-inline: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .sport-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* Highlights list */
  .highlights-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .highlights-list li {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .highlights-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    top: 0.15em;
  }

  .highlight-featured {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md) var(--space-sm) calc(var(--space-md) + 1.5rem);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    margin-block: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .highlight-featured::before {
    left: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* Gallery */
  .gallery-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .gallery-title {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .gallery-item {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .gallery-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 400ms ease;
  }

  .gallery-item:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .gallery-item--wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .gallery-item--wide img {
    height: 360px;
  }

  .gallery-item--accent {
    position: relative;
  }

  .gallery-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(44, 24, 16, 0.75));
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Goals */
  .goals-box {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .goals-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .goals-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .goals-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .goals-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    top: 0.1em;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .gallery-item--wide {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sport-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sport-hero-img {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .gallery-item--wide {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .gallery-item--wide img {
      height: 260px;
    }
  }
</style>
